args.justification: The relation represents a biological entity undergoing a process (process participation), not exerting agency in a causal sense. Using rel_cls_group='PARTICIPATION' more accurately reflects that this edge encodes involvement in a process rather than an agent-causes-event pattern.
args.remark: Relabeled rel_cls_group from AGENCY to PARTICIPATION to align with process_participation_relation semantics.
